room_title: Escape room "Spellbound" by Escape Room 831 in Salinas
room_description: When Riverside was founded, the settlers discovered a woman living alone in the woods. They believe that she was a witch, stormed her cottage, and cast her from the village. Try as they might they were never able to destroy her cottage, and it stands to this day. None who have dared to enter have returned. Can you break the witchâ€™s curse?
